content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #89524 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

I can reproduce when using the specified version of the crate (0.9.3, dated 2019), the issue disappears with the latest (as of today) version 0.11.
I can also reproduce by compiling the config crate itself (with the suggested profile.release configuration), so I /think/ the issue is when compiling one of the dependencies.

Tried to investigate further by compiling its dependencies, I was stopped with compiling errors at serde=1.0.8(very old version).

For this reason I'd tend for a P-medium
